page.title: 20Working On The Rectangle
page.content: Two of the compilers live in our rectangle. Rebecca Davis lives at Langore and Bonny Shanks lives at Little Athill.Amanda Frain moved from our rectangle recently.Our teacher found it very difficult to organise child coverage of the area but we helped him along.The Head Compiler was Victoria Whitaker,ably assisted by Sharon Jasper and Donna Nuttley.Other helpers were Donna Volz, Amanda Frain, Jason Woodridge and Ashley Crawshaw.We found it difficult to decide on suitable keywords.We have enjoyed going out visiting places and have learned much more about our area because of our visits.It would be hard to imagine what our area will be like nine hundred years from now.
